INSERT INTO `chat_messages` VALUES (1,12,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 13:54:52'),(2,12,'assistant','I\'m glad you came to us for a pick-me-up! 😊 Based on your mood, I\'d like to recommend:\n\n1. **The Sexpert** - A light-hearted and fun movie that\'s sure to lift your spirits.\n2. **Hoppers** - A hilarious comedy that will make you laugh out loud.\n3. **The Hayseed** - A classic comedy with a dash of humor and wit.\n\nThese movies are just what you need to brighten up your day!','2026-03-29 13:54:52'),(3,13,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 15:25:30'),(4,13,'assistant','I\'ve got just the thing for you!\n\nHere are three hilarious comedies from our database:\n\n1. \"The Hayseed\" - A lighthearted and entertaining film to lift your spirits.\n2. \"Hoppers\" - A funny and quirky movie that\'s sure to put a smile on your face.\n3. \"Send Help\" - A comedy with a dash of humor and wit, perfect for a pick-me-up.\n\nHope these make you laugh away your sadness!','2026-03-29 15:25:30'),(5,13,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 15:31:38'),(6,13,'assistant','Same as before!\n\nHere are the same three hilarious comedies from our database:\n\n1. \"The Hayseed\"\n2. \"Hoppers\"\n3. \"Send Help\"\n\nHope they bring a smile to your face and brighten up your day!','2026-03-29 15:31:38'),(7,13,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 15:32:56'),(8,13,'assistant','I\'ve got the same three recommendations for you:\n\n1. \"The Hayseed\" - A fun and lighthearted film.\n2. \"Hoppers\" - Quirky humor to lift your spirits.\n3. \"Send Help\" - Comedy with a dash of wit.\n\nHope they help take your mind off things!','2026-03-29 15:32:56'),(9,14,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 15:56:09'),(10,14,'assistant','Feeling down and need a pick-me-up. Let\'s get some laughs in with these comedies:\n\n1. **The Sexpert** - A hilarious take on relationships and sex.\n2. **Hoppers** - Quirky humor and lovable characters will make you smile.\n\nHope these movies put a big grin back on your face!','2026-03-29 15:56:09'),(11,15,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 15:57:22'),(12,15,'assistant','I\'ve got just the thing for you! Since you\'re in the mood for comedies and it\'s a tough day, I\'d like to recommend:\n\n1. \"The Sexpert\"\n2. \"Hoppers\"\n\nThese two movies are sure to put a smile on your face and take your mind off things. Give \'em a try!','2026-03-29 15:57:22'),(13,16,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 16:12:57'),(14,16,'assistant','I\'d be happy to help you brighten up your day with some laughs!\n\nHere are my top comedy picks from our database:\n\n1. **The Sexpert** - A hilarious romantic comedy that\'s sure to put a smile on your face!\n2. **Hoppers** - A lighthearted and entertaining film that\'s perfect for a pick-me-up.\n3. **Send Help** - A comedic take on everyday life that\'s relatable and funny!\n\nHope these suggestions make you laugh and lift your spirits!','2026-03-29 16:12:57'),(15,17,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 16:16:33'),(16,17,'assistant','Feeling down can be tough. Let\'s lift that mood with some laughs! Here are a few comedies from our database:\n\n1. \"The Sexpert\"\n2. \"Hoppers\"\n\nBoth of these films are sure to bring a smile to your face. I hope they help brighten up your day!','2026-03-29 16:16:33'),(17,18,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 16:20:39'),(18,18,'assistant','Sorry to hear that you\'re feeling down 😔. Let\'s brighten things up with some comedies! Here are my top picks from the MovieFlix database:\n\n1. \"The Sexpert\" - a hilarious film that will surely make you laugh.\n2. \"Hoppers\" - an entertaining comedy that\'s sure to lift your mood.\n\nHope these recommendations put a smile on your face!','2026-03-29 16:20:39'),(19,19,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 16:31:49'),(20,19,'assistant','Don\'t be blue for long! 😊 I\'ve got just the thing for you. Here are some comedies from our database that might lift your spirits:\n\n1. \"The Sexpert\"\n2. \"Hoppers\"\n\nHope these movies make you laugh and forget about those blues! 🎬','2026-03-29 16:31:49'),(21,20,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-29 16:37:08'),(22,20,'assistant','Sorry to hear that you\'re feeling down! But don\'t worry, I\'ve got just the thing to lift your spirits! Here are my top picks for comedy movies from our database:\n\n1. **The Sexpert** - a hilarious and quirky film that\'s sure to put a smile on your face.\n2. **Hoppers** - a fun and lighthearted movie that\'s perfect for when you need a laugh.\n\nI hope these recommendations help take your mind off things and leave you feeling brighter!','2026-03-29 16:37:08'),(23,20,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some action movies now','2026-03-31 05:13:29'),(24,20,'assistant','Sorry to hear that you\'re feeling down! But don\'t worry, I\'ve got just the thing to get those endorphins pumping! Here are my top picks for action movies from our database:\n\n1. **Avengers: Infinity War** - an epic superhero showdown that\'s sure to take your mind off things.\n2. **Spider-Man: Far From Home** - a thrilling adventure with plenty of action and excitement.\n\nI hope these recommendations help distract you from feeling sad and get you pumped up!','2026-03-31 05:13:29'),(25,21,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some comedy movies now','2026-03-31 05:23:05'),(26,21,'assistant','Feeling down, eh? Don\'t worry, I\'ve got just the thing to lift your spirits! Here are my top picks for comedies from our database:\n\n1. **The Hayseed** - a classic comedy about a city slicker who gets caught up in rural shenanigans.\n2. **Hoppers** - a hilarious film that\'s sure to make you laugh out loud.\n\nHope these recommendations put a smile on your face!','2026-03-31 05:23:05'),(27,21,'user','hello, today i\'m very sad so i want watch some sci-fi movies now','2026-03-31 05:30:27'),(28,21,'assistant','Feeling down, eh? Sci-fi can be a great escape from reality. Here are my top picks for sci-fi from our database:\n\n1. **Avengers: Infinity War** - an epic battle of good vs. evil in the Marvel universe.\n2. **Spider-Man: Far From Home** - a superhero adventure that\'s sure to take your mind off things.\n\nHope these recommendations transport you to another world!','2026-03-31 05:30:27'),(29,20,'user','I watched a movie years ago about a man who gets stuck in a time loop and keeps reliving the same day over and over again, what is the name of that movie?','2026-03-31 06:43:43'),(30,20,'assistant','That sounds like a mind-bending plot! Unfortunately, I couldn\'t find any matches for that specific plot in our database. However, one movie that comes to mind based on my general knowledge is **Edge of Tomorrow** (not in our database) and another possibility is **The Man Who Replaced Himself** (in our database), but it\'s not exactly about a man stuck in a time loop.\n\nI couldn\'t find an exact match in our database, but here are some other movies that might interest you:\n\n1. **Your Heart Will Be Broken**\n2. **Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man**\n3. **Avatar: Fire and Ash**','2026-03-31 06:43:43'),(31,20,'user','can you recommend for me some romance movies have high rating scores','2026-04-14 09:43:36'),(32,20,'assistant','I\'d be delighted to! Here are my top picks for romance movies from our database with high rating scores:\n\n1. **The Art of Racing in the Rain** - a heartwarming tale of love and loss, told through the eyes of a loyal golden retriever.\n2. **After