ates of America','en','Animation, Family, Drama','Matthew Broderick, Moira Kelly, Nathan Lane, Ernie Sabella, James Earl Jones','Roger Allers, Rob Minkoff','Young lion prince Simba, eager to one day become king of the Pride Lands, grows up under the watchful eye of his father Mufasa; all the while his villainous uncle Scar conspires to take the throne for himself. Amid betrayal and tragedy, Simba must confront his past and find his rightful place in the Circle of Life.',8.3,19555,23.309,'2026-04-14 09:09:04','UgjEj5mXLlk','/sKCr78MXSLixwmZ8DyJLrpMsd15.jpg'),(8966,'Twilight','Twilight',2008,122,'United Kingdom','en','Fantasy, Drama, Romance','Kristen Stewart, Robert Pattinson, Billy Burke, Peter Facinelli, Ashley Greene','Catherine Hardwicke','When Bella Swan moves to a small town in the Pacific Northwest, she falls in love with Edward Cullen, a mysterious classmate who reveals himself to be a 108-year-old vampire. Despite Edward\'s repeated cautions, Bella can\'t stay away from him, a fatal move that endangers her own life.',6.3,14315,17.598,'2026-04-14 09:10:32','nxvGVSc6Ls8','/3Gkb6jm6962ADUPaCBqzz9CTbn9.jpg'),(9702,'Bound by Honor','Bound by Honor',1993,190,'United States of America','en','Crime, Drama, Thriller','Damian Chapa, Jesse Borrego, Benjamin Bratt, Enrique Castillo, Victor Rivers','Taylor Hackford','Based on the true life experiences of poet Jimmy Santiago Baca, the film focuses on half-brothers Paco and Cruz, and their bi-racial cousin Miklo. It opens in 1972, as the three are members of an East L.A. gang known as the \"Vatos Locos\", and the story focuses on how a violent crime and the influence of narcotics alter their lives. Miklo is incarcerated and sent to San Quentin, where he makes a \"home\" for himself. Cruz becomes an exceptional artist, but a heroin addiction overcomes him with tragic results. Paco becomes a cop and an enemy to his \"carnal\", Miklo.',8.1,1500,5.548,'2026-04-14 09:09:52','NMj89zgI8Yc','/gvP6R6juhe2IpCG7QGDgjyUvm0g.jpg'),(10098,'The Kid','The Kid',1921,68,'United States of America','en','Comedy, Drama','Charlie Chaplin, Jackie Coogan, Carl Miller, Edna Purviance, Albert Austin','Charlie Chaplin','A tramp cares for a boy after he\'s abandoned as a newborn by his mother. Later the mother has a change of heart and aches to be reunited with her son.',8.1,2348,4.375,'2026-04-14 09:09:50','O5WXokyub-4','/A9NWYyn7eX0H9XIjaOvfWJ9mCGA.jpg'),(10376,'The Legend of 1900','La leggenda del pianista sull\'oceano',1998,170,'Italy','it','Drama, Music','Tim Roth, Pruitt Taylor Vince, Mélanie Thierry, Bill Nunn, Gabriele Lavia','Giuseppe Tornatore','Musician Max Tooney goes to sell his prized Conn trumpet to a music shop, where he plays the instrument one last time. The shopkeeper recognises the song as one on a record matrix he found and asks who the piece is by. Tooney tells the story of an infant found abandoned in the first class dining room of the four-stacker ocean-liner SS Virginian on 1 January 1900. Danny Boodman, a coal-man from the boiler room, names the boy Danny Boodman T. D. Lemon 1900, after himself, the fruit crate the boy was found in, and the year, and raises him as his own.',8.2,2424,6.266,'2026-04-14 09:09:06','jqhbOiF9-8g','/iOcbJ5pxokOPDRgieVDbsFMrCc6.jpg'),(10494,'Perfect Blue','PERFECT BLUE',1998,82,'Japan','ja','Animation, Thriller','Junko Iwao, Rica Matsumoto, Shiho Niiyama, Masaaki Okura, Shinpachi Tsuji','Satoshi Kon','Rising pop star Mima quits singing to pursue a career as an actress. After she takes up a role on a popular detective show, her handlers and collaborators begin turning up murdered. Harboring feelings of guilt and haunted by visions of her former self, Mima\'s reality and fantasy meld into a frenzied paranoia.',8.3,3125,11.812,'2026-04-14 09:08:47','RrWausp8zDQ','/6WTiOCfDPP8XV4jqfloiVWf7KHq.jpg'),(10528,'Sherlock Holmes','Sherlock Holmes',2009,129,'United States of America','en','Adventure, Crime, Mystery','Robert Downey Jr., Jude Law, Rachel McAdams, Mark Strong, Eddie Marsan','Guy Ritchie','Eccentric consulting detective Sherlock Holmes and Doctor John Watson battle to bring down a new nemesis and unravel a deadly plot that could destroy England.',7.2,14645,51.266,'2026-03-27 07:49:17','zBQfbc1t_I8','/momkKuWburNTqKBF6ez7rvhYVhE.jpg'),(10538,'Passenger 57','Passenger 57',1992,84,'United States of America','en','Action, Adventure, Thriller','Wesley Snipes, Bruce Payne, Tom Sizemore, Alex Datcher, Bruce Greenwood','Kevin Hooks','Airline security specialist John Cutter, finally returning to the job after his wife\'s death, finds himself stuck on a flight being hijacked by notorious terrorist Charles Rane. Unfortunately for the terrorists, they\'re also stuck with him.',6.0,1098,31.652,'2026-03-27 07:49:41','cqftFJdAvtQ','/4VBN8pQxGHjeZWcNv1V1xSw0OKC.jpg'),(10681,'WALL·E','WALL·E',2008,98,'United States of America','en','Animation, Family, Science Fiction','Ben Burtt, Elissa Knight, Jeff Garlin, Fred Willard, John Ratzenberger','Andrew Stanton','After hundreds of years doing what he was built for, WALL•E— a robot designed to clean up the earth—discovers a new purpose in life when he meets a sleek search robot named EVE. EVE comes to realize that WALL•E has inadvertently stumbled upon the key to the planet\'s future, and races back to space to report to the humans. Meanwhile, WALL•E chases EVE across the galaxy and sets into motion one of the most imaginative adventures ever brought to the big screen.',8.1,20100,16.046,'2026-04-14 09:10:04','Tbr_L9Gap_M','/hbhFnRzzg6ZDmm8YAmxBnQpQIPh.jpg'),(10950,'I Am Sam','I Am Sam',2001,132,'United States of America','en','Drama','Sean Penn, Michelle Pfeiffer, Dianne Wiest, Dakota Fanning, Richard Schiff','Jessie Nelson','Sam, a neurodivergent man, has a daughter with a homeless woman who abandons them when they leave the hospital, leaving Sam to raise Lucy on his own. But as Lucy grows up, Sam\'s limitations as a parent start to become a problem and the authorities take her away. Sam convinces high-priced lawyer Rita to take his case pro bono and in turn teaches her the value of love and family.',7.6,2462,29.517,'2026-03-27 07:50:23','z_AguDqCBvo','/8n8BTMIRPKT0KZKSa0nACG9cQ8O.jpg'),(11216,'Cinema Paradiso','Nuovo Cinema Paradiso',1988,124,'Italy','it','Drama, Romance','Philippe Noiret, Jacques Perrin, Marco Leonardi, Salvatore Cascio, Agnese Nano','Giuseppe Tornatore','A filmmaker recalls his childhood, when he fell in love with the movies at his village\'s theater and formed a deep friendship with the theater\'s projectionist.',8.4,4782,10.434,'2026-04-14 09:08:33','JMyVSD6OvO8','/gCI2AeMV4IHSewhJkzsur5MEp6R.jpg'),(11235,'Local Hero','Local Hero',1983,111,'United Kingdom','en','Comedy, Drama','Burt Lancaster, Peter Riegert, Denis Lawson, Fulton Mackay, Peter Capaldi','Bill Forsyth','An American oil company sends a man to Scotland to buy up an entire village where they want to build a refinery. But things don\'t go as expected.',6.8,392,43.174,'2026-03-27 07:49:14','VCFhg6Q6gXU','/jqxD0H9a1rg5bXftsm6gsNOjt4n.jpg'),(11324,'Shutter Island','Shutter Island',2010,138,'United States of America','en','Drama, Thriller, Mystery','Leonardo DiCaprio, Mark Ruffalo, Ben Kingsley, Max von Sydow, Michelle Williams','Martin Scorsese','World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.',8.2,25649,18.736,'2026-04-14 09:09:27','qdPw9x9h5CY','/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg'),(11851,'The Presidio','The Presidio',1988,97,'United States of America','en','Action, Crime, Mystery, Thriller','Sean Connery, Mark Harmon, Meg Ryan, Jack Warden, Mark Blum','Peter Hyams','Jay Austin is now a civilian police detective. Colonel Caldwell was his commanding officer years before when he left the military police over a disagreement over the handling of a drunk driver. Now a series of murders that cross jurisdictions 