rn','Gary Cooper, Ingrid Bergman, Flora Robson, Jerry Austin, John Warburton','Sam Wood','An opportunistic Texas gambler and the exiled Creole daughter of an aristocratic family join forces to achieve justice from the society that has ostracized them.',5.7,15,20.223,'2026-03-27 07:50:27',NULL,NULL),(46738,'Incendies','Incendies',2010,131,'Canada','fr','Drama, War, Mystery','Lubna Azabal, Mélissa Désormeaux-Poulin, Maxim Gaudette, Rémy Girard, Allen Altman','Denis Villeneuve','A mother\'s last wishes send twins Jeanne and Simon on a journey to Middle East in search of their tangled roots. Adapted from Wajdi Mouawad\'s acclaimed play, Incendies tells the powerful and moving tale of two young adults\' voyage to the core of deep-rooted hatred, never-ending wars and enduring love.',8.1,3221,7.604,'2026-04-14 09:10:09','XJ69WnwvZhE','/yH6DAQVgbyj72S66gN4WWVoTjuf.jpg'),(50014,'The Help','The Help',2011,146,'United States of America','en','Drama','Emma Stone, Viola Davis, Bryce Dallas Howard, Octavia Spencer, Jessica Chastain','Tate Taylor','Aibileen Clark is a middle-aged African-American maid who has spent her life raising white children and has recently lost her only son; Minny Jackson is an African-American maid who has often offended her employers despite her family\'s struggles with money and her desperate need for jobs; and Eugenia \"Skeeter\" Phelan is a young white woman who has recently moved back home after graduating college to find out her childhood maid has mysteriously disappeared. These three stories intertwine to explain how life in Jackson, Mississippi revolves around \"the help\"; yet they are always kept at a certain distance because of racial lines.',8.2,8941,11.404,'2026-04-14 09:09:28','3eajzW3XW7Q','/3kmfoWWEc9Vtyuaf9v5VipRgdjx.jpg'),(50619,'The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1','The Twilight Saga: Breaking Dawn - Part 1',2011,117,'United States of America','en','Adventure, Fantasy, Romance','Kristen Stewart, Robert Pattinson, Taylor Lautner, Bi