ion, a young grifter named Estella is determined to make a name for herself with her designs. She befriends a pair of young thieves who appreciate her appetite for mischief, and together they are able to build a life for themselves on the London streets. One day, Estella’s flair for fashion catches the eye of the Baroness von Hellman, a fashion legend who is devastatingly chic and terrifyingly haute. But their relationship sets in motion a course of events and revelations that will cause Estella to embrace her wicked side and become the raucous, fashionable and revenge-bent Cruella.',8.0,9983,22.690,'2026-04-14 09:07:53','jpZrVxvG3mk','/hjS9mH8KvRiGHgjk6VUZH7OT0Ng.jpg'),(341553,'Countess Dora','Kontesa Dora',1990,117,'Croatia','hr','Drama','Alma Prica, Rade Šerbedžija, Irina Alfyorova, Relja Bašić, Božidar Boban','Zvonimir Berković','A pseudo biography of Dora Pejačević (10 September 1885 - 5 March 1923), a Croatian composer.',5.0,1,37.270,'2026-03-27 07:49:39',NULL,'/fe0g1jvlspTWTbeRpi5S9ecHstM.jpg'),(346698,'Barbie','Barbie',2023,114,'United Kingdom','en','Comedy, Adventure','Margot Robbie, Ryan Gosling, America Ferrera, Ariana Greenblatt, Issa Rae','Greta Gerwig','Barbie and Ken are having the time of their lives in the colorful and seemingly perfect world of Barbie Land. However, when they get a chance to go to the real world, they soon discover the joys and perils of living among humans.',6.9,10955,22.955,'2026-04-14 09:08:17','Y1IgAEejvqM','/iuFNMS8U5cb6xfzi51Dbkovj7vM.jpg'),(354912,'Coco','Coco',2017,105,'United States of America','en','Family, Animation, Music, Adventure','Anthony Gonzalez, Gael García Bernal, Benjamin Bratt, Alanna Ubach, Renée Victor','Lee Unkrich','Despite his family’s baffling generations-old ban on music, Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol, Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel\'s family history.',8.2,20813,21.761,'2026-04-14 09:08:17','Rvr68u6k5sI','/6Ryitt95xrO8KXuqRGm1fUuNwqF.jpg'),(361743,'Top Gun: Maverick','Top Gun: Maverick',2022,131,'United States of America','en','Action, Drama','Tom Cruise, Val Kilmer, Miles Teller, Jennifer Connelly, Bashir Salahuddin','Joseph Kosinski','After more than thirty years of service as one of the Navy’s top aviators, and dodging the advancement in rank that would ground him, Pete “Maverick” Mitchell finds himself training a detachment of TOP GUN graduates for a specialized mission the likes of which no living pilot has ever seen.',8.2,10755,21.075,'2026-03-28 06:46:06','ODZMo8HXqwA','/62HCnUTziyWcpDaBO2i1DX17ljH.jpg'),(366232,'ErOddity(s) 2','ErOddity(s) 2',2015,94,'United States of America','en','Drama, Horror, Science Fiction','Addison Graham, Grayson Lange, Cory Tyndall, Clay Yearwood, Walter Delmar','Steven Vasquez','ErOddity(s) 2 follows the lives of several gay youths and adults as they discover a world of the odd, the erotic and the supernatural, all of it in three short films. First, a Texas teen and wanna be actor knocks them dead at \"The Audition\". Second, two soldiers are on a secret mission in the jungles of South America. Once captured, their last night together will reveal dark secrets and create sexual tensions that will cause wide spread collateral damage in \"The Private War of Joseph Sargent\". And finally, in \"The Caretaker of Cook County\", a cemetery worker hides his recent disfigurement under the cloak of a sinister hood. But it doesn\'t hide his twisted attempt to recapture the one that got away. An attempt that includes the help from young male bodies fresh from the mortuary!',3.9,13,27.088,'2026-03-27 07:49:57','Dv4Th2NbubY','/qoWm1et3sBXmdjCwybHFGTNw8Gt.jpg'),(372058,'Your Name.','君の名は。',2016,106,'Japan','ja','Animation, Romance, Drama','Ryunosuke Kamiki, Mone Kamishiraishi, Ryo Narita, Aoi Yuuki, Nobunaga Shimazaki','Makoto Shinkai','High schoolers Mitsuha and Taki are complete strangers living separate lives. But one night, they suddenly switch places. Mitsuha wakes up in Taki’s body, and he in hers. This bizarre occurrence continues to happen randomly, and the two must adjust their lives around each other.',8.5,12418,27.191,'2026-04-14 09:08:03','o4-URMnBOPU','/q719jXXEzOoYaps6babgKnONONX.jpg'),(372754,'Dou kyu sei – Classmates','同級生',2016,61,'Japan','ja','Romance, Animation','Kenji Nojima, Hiroshi Kamiya, Hideo Ishikawa, Yurino','Shoko Nakamura','Rihito Sajo, an honor student with a perfect score on the entrance exam and Hikaru Kusakabe, in a band and popular among girls, would have never crossed paths. Until one day they started talking at the practice for their school’s upcoming chorus festival. After school, the two meet regularly, as Hikaru helps Rihito to improve his singing skills. While they listen to each other’s voice and harmonize, their hearts start to beat together.',8.3,434,5.294,'2026-04-14 09:08:46','wFQTncSyukA','/cIfRCA5wEvj9tApca4UDUagQEiM.jpg'),(374720,'Dunkirk','Dunkirk',2017,107,'United Kingdom','en','War, Action, Drama','Fionn Whitehead, Tom Hardy, Mark Rylance, Kenneth Branagh, Cillian Murphy','Christopher Nolan','The story of the miraculous evacuation of Allied soldiers from Belgium, Britain, Canada and France, who were cut off and surrounded by the German army from the beaches and harbour of Dunkirk between May 26th and June 4th 1940 during World War II.',7.5,17407,54.986,'2026-03-28 06:46:12','T7O7BtBnsG4','/b4Oe15CGLL61Ped0RAS9JpqdmCt.jpg'),(378064,'A Silent Voice: The Movie','映画 聲の形',2016,129,'Japan','ja','Animation, Drama, Romance','Miyu Irino, Saori Hayami, Aoi Yuuki, Kensho Ono, Yuki Kaneko','Naoko Yamada','Shouya Ishida starts bullying the new girl in class, Shouko Nishimiya, because she is deaf. But as the teasing continues, the rest of the class starts to turn on Shouya for his lack of compassion. When they leave elementary school, Shouko and Shouya do not speak to each other again... until an older, wiser Shouya, tormented by his past behaviour, decides he must see Shouko once more. He wants to atone for his sins, but is it already too late...?',8.4,4431,13.438,'2026-04-14 09:08:35','TQK9By9qQiw','/tuFaWiqX0TXoWu7DGNcmX3UW7sT.jpg'),(378584,'High Tor','High Tor',1956,90,'United States of America','en','Fantasy, Music','Bing Crosby, Julie Andrews, Nancy Olson, Everett Sloane, Hans Conried','James Neilson, Franklin J. Schaffner','High Tor is a 1936 play by Maxwell Anderson. Twenty years after the original production, Anderson adapted it into a television musical with Arthur Schwartz.  Anderson first considered a musical adaptation of High Tor for television in 1949. He and John Monks Jr. adapted the play as a made-for-television musical fantasy in 1955, with music by Arthur Schwartz and lyrics by Anderson. High Tor was filmed in November 1955 by Desilu Productions at the RKO-Pathé Studio and broadcast March 10, 1956 on the CBS television network, as a 90-minute episode of the series Ford Star Jubilee. Bing Crosby, Julie Andrews, Nancy Olson, Hans Conreid, and Keenan Wynn starred in the film, produced by Arthur Schwartz, and directed by James Neilson.',7.5,2,32.983,'2026-03-27 07:49:50',NULL,'/yb0uOPNN2xipDWvuy8GE9JvA1OG.jpg'),(386948,'Beautiful Brazil','Beautiful Brazil',1952,8,'United States of America','en','Documentary','James A. FitzPatrick','','We start in Rio de Janeiro, with the statue of Cristo Redentor on Mount Corcovado, the avenue along the beach, the beauty of an historic city, and the landmark, Sugarloaf. Brazil\'s 47 million people celebrate racial diversity. From the Copacabana, we travel 40 miles to a resort, Quitandinha, where President Truman spoke. Then it\'s on to Sao Paulo, a modern, industrial city, and finally to the spectacular waterfalls of Iguazu on the border between Brazil and Argentina.',0.0,0,23.011,'2026-03-27 07:50:26',NULL,NULL),(387006,'Imperial Delhi','Imperial Delhi',1939,9,'United States of America','en','Documentary','James A. FitzPatrick','','This MGM short, part of James A. Fitzpatrick\'s Traveltalk series, takes the viewer to the capital of British India, Delhi. Visits to mosques and temples are followed by a tour of the shopping district, Chandni Chowk. The streets are filled bullock carts and only a few cars. Much is made of the peaceful co-existence between Hindu and Muslim. This is followed by a visit to the Viceroy\'s palace in adjoining New Delhi with a taste of the pomp and majesty of Imperial India.',0.0,0,33.627,'2026-03-28 06:45:43',NULL,'/qJOkKw3jquQrKxjp2iyYJMeMJiL.jpg'),(396535,'Train to Busan','부산행',2016,118,'South Korea','ko','Horror, Thriller, Action, Adventure','Gong Yoo, Kim Su-an, Jung Yu-mi, Don Lee, Choi Woo-shik','Yeon Sang-ho','When a zombie virus pushes Korea into a state of emergency, those trapped on an express train to Busan must fight for their own survival.',7.7,8277,18.378,'2026-04-14 09:07:57','0_sV9luPnMk','/vNVFt6dtcqnI7hqa6LFBUibuFiw.jpg'),(398818,'Call Me by Your Name','Call Me by Your Name',2017,132,'Brazil','en','Romance, Drama','Armie Hammer, Timothée Chalamet, Michael Stuhlbarg, Amira Casar, Esther Garrel','Luca Guadagnino','In the summer of 1983, a 17-year-old Elio spends his days in his family\'s villa in Italy. One day Oliver, a graduate student, arrives to assist Elio\'s father, a professor of Greco-Roman culture. Soon, Elio and Oliver discover a summer that will alter their lives forever.',8.1,12682,9.276,'2026-04-14 09:10:15','Z9AYPxH5NTM','/mZ4gBdfkhP9tvLH1DO4m4HYtiyi.jpg'),(399106,'Piper','Piper',2016,6,'United States of America','en','Family, Animation','','Alan Barillaro','A mother bird tries to teach her little one how to find food by herself. In the process, she encounters a traumatic experience that she must overcome in order to survive.',8.1,1723,1.735,'2026-04-14 09:09:46','DW8T9nvitLI','/5fu2d8