s.',5.9,25,20.754,'2026-04-14 09:07:56','aSfs0peFoEo','/uNTZ9vp32AYd6kcAcm63jVg6u44.jpg'),(406997,'Wonder','Wonder',2017,113,'United States of America','en','Family, Drama','Jacob Tremblay, Julia Roberts, Owen Wilson, Izabela Vidovic, Noah Jupe','Stephen Chbosky','The story of August Pullman – a boy with facial differences – who enters fifth grade, attending a mainstream elementary school for the first time.',8.1,8217,8.755,'2026-04-14 09:10:05','ASAGdtAJPnU','/sONh3LYGFcVDTy8pm1tbSOB13Li.jpg'),(411135,'Future World','Future World',2018,88,'United States of America','en','Science Fiction','James Franco, Suki Waterhouse, Jeffrey Wahlberg, Margarita Levieva, Snoop Dogg','Bruce Thierry Cheung, James Franco','A young boy searches a future world wasteland for a rumored cure for his dying mother.',4.3,276,34.323,'2026-03-27 07:49:44','uljtvXrkdbc','/kMA0IalnEEa0PaHRUzzjpTu5xXQ.jpg'),(414419,'Kill Bill: The Whole Bloody Affair','Kill Bill: The Whole Bloody Affair',2011,253,'United States of America','en','Action, Crime','Uma Thurman, Lucy Liu, Vivica A. Fox, Michael Madsen, Daryl Hannah','Quentin Tarantino','Quentin Tarantino\'s complete cut combining Kill Bill: Vol. 1 and Vol. 2 follows The Bride, a former assassin who awakens from a four-year coma after being shot by her mentor and lover, Bill. She embarks on a vengeful quest to eliminate Bill and the Deadly Viper Assassination Squad who betrayed her.',8.1,1203,11.102,'2026-04-14 09:11:04','7SLysSldjtc','/nSOJfWJCdVFZQwXQA7RXn7FIIiY.jpg'),(425274,'Now You See Me: Now You Don\'t','Now You See Me: Now You Don\'t',2025,113,'United States of America','en','Thriller, Crime','Jesse Eisenberg, Dominic Sessa, Ariana Greenblatt, Justice Smith, Rosamund Pike','Ruben Fleischer','The original Four Horsemen reunite with a new generation of illusionists to take on powerful diamond heiress Veronika Vanderberg, who leads a criminal empire built on money laundering and trafficking. The new and old magicians must overcome their differences to work together on their most ambitious heist yet.',6.5,1369,42.001,'2026-03-27 07:49:27','lLWESUfW-0A','/oD3Eey4e4Z259XLm3eD3WGcoJAh.jpg'),(429617,'Spider-Man: Far From Home','Spider-Man: Far From Home',2019,129,'United States of America','en','Action, Adventure, Science Fiction','Tom Holland, Jake Gyllenhaal, Samuel L. Jackson, Marisa Tomei, Jon Favreau','Jon Watts','Peter Parker and his friends go on a summer trip to Europe. However, they will hardly be able to rest - Peter will have to agree to help Nick Fury uncover the mystery of creatures that cause natural disasters and destruction throughout the continent.',7.4,16774,30.137,'2026-03-27 07:50:12','LFoz8ZJWmPs','/4q2NNj4S5dG2RLF9CpXsej7yXl.jpg'),(438631,'Dune','Dune',2021,155,'United States of America','en','Science Fiction, Adventure','Timothée Chalamet, Rebecca Ferguson, Oscar Isaac, Jason Momoa, Stellan Skarsgård','Denis Villeneuve','Paul Atreides, a brilliant and gifted young man born into a great destiny beyond his understanding, must travel to the most dangerous planet in the universe to ensure the future of his family and his people. As malevolent forces explode into conflict over the planet\'s exclusive supply of the most precious resource in existence-a commodity capable of unlocking humanity\'s greatest potential-only those who can conquer their fear will survive.',7.8,14618,29.588,'2026-03-27 07:50:06','w0HgHet0sxg','/gDzOcq0pfeCeqMBwKIJlSmQpjkZ.jpg'),(439079,'The Nun','The Nun',2018,96,'United States of America','en','Horror','Taissa Farmiga, Demián Bichir, Bonnie Aarons, Jonas Bloquet, Ingrid Bisu','Corin Hardy','A priest with a dark past and a novice nearing her final vows are sent by the Vatican to Romania to investigate a nun\'s death and face a demonic force.',5.9,7127,21.118,'2026-04-14 09:07:44','UvMVjwwZOF4','/sFC1ElvoKGdHJIWRpNB3xWJ9lJA.jpg'),(441130,'Wolfwalkers','Wolfwalkers',2020,102,'France','en','Animation, Family, Adventure, Fantasy','Honor Kneafsey, Eva Whittaker, Sean Bean, Simon McBurney, Tommy Tiernan','Tomm Moore, Ross Stewart','In a time of superstition and magic, when wolves are seen as demonic and nature an evil to be tamed, a young apprentice hunter comes to Ireland with her father to wipe out the last pack. But when she saves a wild native girl, their friendship leads her to discover the world of the Wolfwalkers and transform her into the very thing her father is tasked to destroy.',8.2,1356,5.431,'2026-04-14 09:09:28','d_Z_tybgPgg','/vqGiNbdc2sDwsnivMMYzwAoSSu6.jpg'),(444796,'Maximum Thrust','Maximum Thrust',2003,90,'United States of America','en','Drama, Action','Beverly Lynne, Aaron Brumfield, Robyn Hyden, Akira Lane, Nicole Oring','Paul Miller','A down and out all girl race team, Maximum Thrust, hires a sexy newbie street racer, Bekka (Beverly Lynne), in hopes of saving a failing business and salvaging street creds and respect. The action is fast and furious on and off the track when Bekka is seduced by a rival racer, Junior Sloan. When it is discovered Junior intends on destroying Maximum Thrust, even if it means killing the driver, Bekka reunites with the team. With friends and lovers helping, the women of Maximum Thrust build an awesome street racing machine and lay it all on the line when they challenge Junior to a race at \"Street Wars.\" It is a high octane battle where Bekka blows by Junior and stops him on the track. Using intimate information, Bekka and the team have Junior arrested and the team reigns as the Street Wars champions.',3.4,7,30.069,'2026-03-27 07:49:59',NULL,'/d6bphdrGs94Eu18scaEQ4IbMOnM.jpg'),(447362,'Life in a Year','Life in a Year',2020,107,'United States of America','en','Drama, Romance','Jaden Smith, Cara Delevingne, Cuba Gooding Jr., Chris D\'Elia, JT Neal','Mitja Okorn','A 17 year old finds out that his girlfriend is dying, so he sets out to give her an entire life, in the last year she has left.',8.2,1956,3.470,'2026-04-14 09:09:09','BgmJ14p4Uuk','/bP7u19opmHXYeTCUwGjlLldmUMc.jpg'),(458220,'Palmer','Palmer',2021,110,'United States of America','en','Drama','Justin Timberlake, Ryder Allen, Juno Temple, Alisha Wainwright, June Squibb','Fisher Stevens','After 12 years in prison, former high school football star Eddie Palmer returns home to put his life back together—and forms an unlikely bond with Sam, an outcast boy from a troubled home. But Eddie\'s past threatens to ruin his new life and family.',8.1,1883,5.321,'2026-04-14 09:10:00','8jVuOheTNGQ','/xSDdRAjxKAGi8fUBLOqSrBhJmF0.jpg'),(467905,'How to Make a Killing','How to Make a Killing',2026,106,'United Kingdom','en','Comedy, Thriller','Glen Powell, Margaret Qualley, Jessica Henwick, Ed Harris, Bill Camp','John Patton Ford','Disowned at birth by his obscenely wealthy family, blue-collar Becket Redfellow will stop at nothing to reclaim his inheritance, no matter how many relatives stand in his way.',7.0,250,33.374,'2026-03-27 07:48:49','B7RslMKZ2Yc','/yQ7OP2HYxl9YmkWNMkuUA2YaF5.jpg'),(475557,'Joker','Joker',2019,122,'Canada','en','Crime, Thriller, Drama','Joaquin Phoenix, Robert De Niro, Zazie Beetz, Frances Conroy, Brett Cullen','Todd Phillips','During the 1980s, a failed stand-up comedian is driven insane and turns to a life of crime and chaos in Gotham City while becoming an infamous psychopathic crime figure.',8.1,27529,18.372,'2026-03-28 06:46:24','-RFFRxcoKfA','/udDclJoHjfjb8Ekgsd4FDteOkCU.jpg'),(476292,'Maquia: When the Promised Flower Blooms','さよならの朝に約束の花をかざろう',2018,115,'Japan','ja','Animation, Fantasy, Drama','Manaka Iwami, Miyu Irino, Yuuki Sakurai, Ai Kayano, Yuki Kaji','Mari Okada','Fleeing the war, the immortal Machia, graced with eternal youth, finds a baby abandoned in the forest and decides to raise it as her own child, sparking a moving story between a mortal and a being who does not age.',8.2,697,5.262,'2026-04-14 09:09:42','I5ke_BwozoI','/hL3NqRE2ccR4Y2sYSJTrmalRjrz.jpg'),(490132,'Green Book','Green Book',2018,130,'United States of America','en','Drama, Comedy, History','Viggo Mortensen, Mahershala Ali, Linda Cardellini, Sebastian Maniscalco, Dimiter D. Marinov','Peter Farrelly','Tony Lip, a bouncer in 1962, is hired to drive pianist Don Shirley on a tour through the Deep South in the days when African Americans, forced to find alternate accommodations and services due to segregation laws below the Mason-Dixon Line, relied on a guide called The Negro Motorist Green Book.',8.2,12743,12.051,'2026-04-14 09:09:13','QkZxoko_HC0','/7BsvSuDQuoqhWmU2fL7W2GOcZHU.jpg'),(493125,'An Affair - Two Sisters','정사-두자매',2017,72,'South Korea','ko','Drama, Romance','Min Do-yoon, Lee Chae-dam, Yoo Ri, Sang Woo, Jo Yong-bok','Park Joo-yeong','Two beautiful sisters run a cabin in the mountains that is well-known to men as a place of affection. An unknown man near the cabin watches them closely.',4.7,3,23.002,'2026-04-14 09:08:19','A0IPYE6rdZk','/hd53bYFpoWjojG08xLQBO8cP50h.jpg'),(496243,'Parasite','기생충',2019,133,'South Korea','ko','Comedy, Thriller, Drama','Song Kang-ho, Lee Sun-kyun, Cho Yeo-jeong, Choi Woo-shik, Park So-dam','Bong Joon Ho','All unemployed, Ki-taek\'s family takes peculiar interest in the wealthy and glamorous Parks for their livelihood until they get entangled in an unexpected incident.',8.5,20406,31.416,'2026-03-27 07:50:39','bM9QabAojCg','/7IiTTgloJzvGI1TAYymCfbfl3vT.jpg'),(498731,'Palimpsests','Palimpsestes',2017,13,'France','fr','Documentary','','Joana Hadjithomas, Khalil Joreige','This film is from the project Unconformities, comprised of artworks made up from the material of surveyed land, extracted from coring construction sites in Paris, Athens and Beirut. These cores bare their \"unconformities\"—temporal ruptures, natural disasters, geological movements—in full view, revealing a constant cycle of construction and deconstruction that is the defining feature of civilisations past and present, with each using the stones of the last. History appears not as layers but as actions, a kind of palimpsest mixing epochs and civilizations. These poetic recompositions question the dominant forms of narrating and representing history, but also address debates around the Anthropocene.',0.0,0,48.978,'2026-03-27 07:49:26',NULL,'/vlgFl5X0VPxNX4hV7sBAVfnkyvt.jpg'),(502356,'The Super Mario Bros. Movie','The Super Mario Bros. Movie',2023,93,'Japan','en','Family, Comedy, Adventure, Animation, Fantasy','Chris Pratt, Anya Taylor-Joy, Charlie Day, Jack Black, Keegan-Michael Key','Aaron Horvath, Michael Jelenic','While working underground to fix a water main, Brooklyn plumbers—and brothers—Mario and Luigi are transported down a mysterious pipe and wander into a magical new world. But when the brothers are separated, Mario embarks on an epic quest to find Luigi.',7.6,10475,324.160,'2026-03-27 07:49:19','RjNcTBXTk4I','/qNBAXBIQlnOThrVvA6mA2B5ggV6.jpg'),(504253,'I Want to Eat Your Pancreas','君の膵臓をたべたい',2018,108,'Japan','ja','Animation, Drama, Romance','Mahiro Takasugi, Lynn, Yukiyo Fujii, Yuma Uchida, Jun Fukushima','Shinichiro Ushijima','After his classmate and crush is diagnosed with a pancreatic disease, an average high schooler sets out to make the most of her final days.',8.2,1754,6.045,'2026-04-14 09:09:12','MONVPR1dnRQ','/qpV8kvRfAntV7D4aOOsLIz7OdPc.jpg'),(508442,'Soul','Soul',2020,101,'United States of America','en','Animation, Family, Drama, Music, Fantasy','Jamie Foxx, Tina Fey, Graham Norton, Rachel House, Alice Braga','Pete Docter','Joe Gardner is a middle school teacher with a love for jazz music. After a successful audition at the Half Note Club, he suddenly gets into an accident that separates his soul from his body and is transported to the You Seminar, a center in which souls develop and gain passions before being transported to a newborn child. Joe must enlist help from the other souls-in-training, like 22, a soul who has spent eons in the You Seminar, in order to get back to Earth.',8.1,11313,11.365,'2026-04-14 09:10:14','Gs--6c7Hn_A','/6jmppcaubzLF8wkXM36ganVISCo.jpg'),(508883,'The Boy and the Heron','君たちはどう生きるか',2023,124,'Japan','ja','Animation, Fantasy, Drama','Soma Santoki, Masaki Suda, Ko Shibasaki, Aimyon, Yoshino Kimura','Hayao Miyazaki','While the Second World War rages, the teenage Mahito, haunted by his mother\'s tragic death, is relocated from Tokyo to the serene rural home of his new stepmother Natsuko, a woman who bears a striking resemblance to the boy\'s mother. As he tries to adjust, this strange new world grows even stranger following the appearance of a persistent gray heron, who perplexes and bedevils Mahito, dubbing him the \"long-awaited one.\"',7.4,2583,11.669,'2026-04-14 09:10:49','A002-b7IH2M','/4GKye5dR4uJyYbcyTveSue1gATD.jpg'),(508947,'Turning Red','Turning Red',2022,100,'United States of America','en','Animation, Family, Comedy, Fantasy','Rosalie Chiang, Sandra Oh, Ava Morse, Hyein Park, Maitreyi Ramakrishnan','Domee Shi','Thirteen-year-old Mei is experiencing the awkwardness of being a teenager with a twist – when she gets too excited, she transforms into a giant red panda.',7.3,5738,21.531,'2026-04-14 09:08:17','XdKzUbAiswE','/qsdjk9oAKSQMWs0Vt5Pyfh6O4GZ.jpg'),(508965,'Klaus','Klaus',2019,97,'Spain','en','Animation, Family, Comedy','Jason Schwartzman, J.K. Simmons, Rashida Jones, Joan Cusack, Norm Macdonald','Sergio Pablos','A selfish postman and a reclusive toymaker form an unlikely friendship, delivering joy to a cold, dark town that desperately needs it.',8.2,4609,5.462,'2026-04-14 09:09:10','taE3PwurhYM','/q125RHUDgR4gjwh1QkfYuJLYkL.jpg'),(512850,'Ošklivá princezna','Ošklivá princezna',1999,NULL,'Czech Republic','cs','Family, Fantasy, TV Movie','Viktor Preiss, Lenka Vlasáková, Sabina Laurinová, Alois Švehlík, Michal Dlouhý','Miroslav Sobota','A fairy-tale comedy about how a king decided to marry off both of his daughters on the same day. Princess Zlata is a true beauty who has no shortage of suitors. Princess Pepička is less fortunate, as fate has blessed her with a good heart and a sharp mind, but has been stingy with beauty. And so the king decided to marry off his adult daughters at the same time and hold both weddings together.',0.0,0,24.379,'2026-03-27 07:50:20',NULL,NULL),(513592,'Vodnická čertovina','Vodnická čertovina',1996,NULL,'Czech Republic','cs','Family, Fantasy, TV Movie','Václav Vydra, Taťjana Medvecká, Miroslav Vladyka, Dagmar Havlová Veškrnová, Ladislav Mrkvička','Vlasta Janečková','When something flashes across the pond dam in the early evening, it could be the gamekeeper Čeřínek, or the poacher Kopýtko and the tailor Nitka, or... could it be Pepík and Franta? A water sprite, no, water sprites don\'t exist, only superstitious old women and the poor fish warden, who is a little scared of guarding the carp in the tower, believe in them. At least that\'s what Kopýtko and Nitka think as they plunder the pond so that their mischievous wives can show off. And what if they manage to catch a colossal fish, a carp bigger than anyone has ever seen before? Immediately, a plan emerges in their greedy minds to pass the carp off as a water sprite, display it in pubs, and make a fortune.',0.0,0,27.517,'2026-03-27 07:49:59',NULL,'/txXk6ke7NdWyjv4Sq4jctnjUXz7.jpg'),(515771,'Lady Bodyguard','Lady Bodyguard',1943,69,'United States of America','en','Comedy','Anne Shirley, Eddie Albert, Raymond Walburn, Roger Pryor, Maude Eburne','William Clemens','A.C.Baker, advertising executive for an insurance company, approaches test pilot Terry Moore with a proposition that in return for using his picture and endorsement he will get a paid-for-a-year $1000 policy. High-risk Terry agrees. George MacAlister fires his secretary, Miss Tracy, just as she is typing up the policy and she, for spite, changes the amount from a thousand dollars to one million dollars. A.C. delivers the policy, without noticing the difference, to Terry at a party at the Frolics Club, a cheap joint wedged between a burlesque house and a flop house hotel. Three characters, an elderly hat-check \"girl\" known as Mother Hodges; Avery Jamieson, a broken-down actor; and bartender Harry Gargan are named beneficiaries. When the company discovers the error, A.C. is sent to get back the policy and, pending that, don\'t let Terry make any test flights.',4.0,2,70.762,'2026-03-27 07:48:58',NULL,'/smwHQgTVMJLCRzjWRaqVQHAZPTz.jpg'),(517302,'Hatching','Pahanhautoja',2022,87,'Belgium','fi','Horror, Fantasy, Drama','Siiri Solalinna, Sophia Heikkilä, Jani Volanen, Reino Nordin, Oiva Ollila','Hanna Bergholm','12 year old Tinja is desperate to please her mother, a woman obsessed with presenting the image of a perfect family. One night, Tinja finds a strange egg. What hatches is beyond belief.',6.3,481,19.976,'2026-04-14 09:08:22','P9zvYdm3JZI','/jgJACjJIpcbFfEEmEglinfQWQPO.jpg'),(517814,'Capernaum','کفرناحوم',2018,126,'France','ar','Drama','Zain Al Rafeea, Yordanos Shifera, Boluwatife Treasure Bankole, Kawsar Al Haddad, Fadi Kamel Yousef','Nadine Labaki','After running away from his negligent parents, committing a violent crime and being sentenced to five years in jail, a hardened, streetwise 12-year-old Lebanese boy sues his parents in protest of the life they have given him.',8.1,1953,3.805,'2026-04-14 09:09:51','maf0AbL3uEw','/mFnfTVADj8yOxwzprYOmTPselk8.jpg'),(519182,'Despicable Me 4','Despicable Me 4',2024,94,'United States of America','en','Family, Comedy, Animation, Science Fiction, Action','Steve Carell, Kristen Wiig, Will Ferrell, Sofía Vergara, Miranda Cosgrove','Chris Renaud','Gru and Lucy and their girls—Margo, Edith and Agnes—welcome a new member to the Gru family, Gru Jr., who is intent on tormenting his dad. Gru also faces a new nemesis in Maxime Le Mal and his femme fatale girlfriend Valentina, forcing the family to go on the run.',7.0,3146,27.663,'2026-04-14 09:07:25','LtNYaH61dXY','/wWba3TaojhK7NdycRhoQpsG0FaH.jpg'),(522924,'The Art of Racing in the Rain','The Art of Racing in the Rain',2019,109,'United States of America','en','Drama, Romance','Kevin Costner, Milo Ventimiglia, Amanda Seyfried, Ryan Kiera Armstrong, Lily Dodsworth-Evans','Simon Curtis','A family dog – with a near-human soul and a philosopher\'s mind – evaluates his life through the lessons learned by his human owner, a race-car driver.',8.2,1659,2.943,'2026-04-14 09:09:37','eaxMiwjrJ3Y','/mi5VN4ww0JZgRFJIaPxxTGKjUg7.jpg'),(527641,'Five Feet Apart','Five Feet Apart',2019,116,'United States of America','en','Romance, Drama','Haley Lu Richardson, Cole Sprouse, Moisés Arias, Kimberly Hébert Gregory, Parminder Nagra','Justin Baldoni','Seventeen-year-old Stella spends most of her time in the hospital as a cystic fibrosis patient. Her life is full of routines, boundaries and self-control — all of which get put to the test when she meets Will, an impossibly charming teen who has the same illness. There\'s an instant flirtation, though restrictions dictate that they must maintain a safe distance between them. As their connection intensifies, so does the temptation to throw the rules out the window and embrace that attraction.',8.2,5887,5.364,'2026-04-14 09:09:16','24YrEAGF32M','/kreTuJBkUjVWePRfhHZuYfhNE1T.jpg'),(531428,'Portrait of a Lady on Fire','Portrait de la jeune fille en feu',2019,121,'France','fr','Drama, Romance','Noémie Merlant, Adèle Haenel, Luàna Bajrami, Valeria Golino, Christel Baras','Céline Sciamma','On an isolated island in Brittany at the end of the eighteenth century, a female painter is obliged to paint a wedding portrait of a young woman.',8.1,2896,7.198,'2026-04-14 09:10:10','R-fQPTwma9o','/2LquGwEhbg3soxSCs9VNyh5VJd9.jpg'),(532639,'Pinocchio','Pinocchio',2022,105,'United States of America','en','Fantasy, Adventure, Family','Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Tom Hanks, Benjamin Evan Ainsworth, Angus Wright, Cynthia Erivo','Robert Zemeckis','A wooden puppet embarks on a thrilling adventure to become a real boy.',6.3,1715,3.476,'2026-04-14 09:11:42','gV_0pYoCssc','/zaZhjKrJeWczQ3AotKoQObppEbH.jpg'),(533514,'Violet Evergarden: The Movie','劇場版 ヴァイオレット・エヴァーガーデン',2020,140,'Japan','ja','Animation, Drama, Fantas