Gaten Matarazzo, Woody Harrelson, Kieran Culkin, Glenn Close','Andy Serkis','A satirical allegory of revolution and power that traces how a movement for equality is systematically corrupted. As the pigs consolidate control, truth is erased, dissent is crushed and the farm descends into a ruthless dictatorship.',0.0,0,4.523,'2026-04-14 09:11:28','NN6J7l6ulYk','/6pzI1DIlxwAFffw9OZcG6cr031U.jpg'),(547012,'Buffaloed','Buffaloed',2020,95,'United States of America','en','Comedy, Drama','Zoey Deutch, Judy Greer, Jermaine Fowler, Jai Courtney, Noah Reid','Tanya Wexler','Set in the underworld of debt-collecting, homegrown hustler Peg Dahl will do anything to escape Buffalo, NY.',6.7,265,63.307,'2026-03-27 07:49:08','LrQZpeMcM5g','/7ecianrsS9xYzqoAtVIW8tMcbIX.jpg'),(547824,'Beautiful Funerals','Beautiful Funerals',1996,2,'United States of America','en','','','Stan Brakhage','BEAUTIFUL FUNERALS is a hand-painted double-step-printed film composed of 1) dense blackness variously punctuated by brilliantly colored jewel/flower-like shapes AND 2) interruptive white sections which are fuzzily dotted with blurred whites and criss-crossed by black \"brushstrokes\" and hard-edge straight black and white lines. Finally there is a brilliant pinkish flare veined with curled blue lines which engenders a resolution between these (above described) alternating modes - colors in the straight-line sections, lines among the artifice of \"flowers,\" a kind of dark lattice-form which knits the two modes, gray and colored \"clouds\" which correlate them.',5.0,3,26.210,'2026-03-28 06:46:13',NULL,'/xWweaDl17GzJtve8CT99lo2UbJ1.jpg'),(552524,'Lilo & Stitch','Lilo & Stitch',2025,108,'United States of America','en','Family, Science Fiction, Comedy','Maia Kealoha, Sydney Agudong, Chris Sanders, Zach Galifianakis, Billy Magnussen','Dean Fleischer Camp','The wildly funny and touching story of a lonely Hawaiian girl and the fugitive alien who helps to mend her broken family.',7.2,2108,24.166,'2026-04-14 09:0