Attila demands of its performers not only passion and confidence, but also the ability to find subtle accents and psychological nuances.',0.0,0,63.430,'2026-03-27 07:49:06',NULL,'/oRoULQnyJldHFdM8aoVhC2AAec7.jpg'),(567609,'Ready or Not','Ready or Not',2019,95,'United States of America','en','Horror, Comedy','Samara Weaving, Mark O\'Brien, Adam Brody, Henry Czerny, Andie MacDowell','Matt Bettinelli-Olpin, Tyler Gillett','A young bride\'s wedding night turns into her worst nightmare when her ridiculously rich in-laws force her to play a gruesome game of hide-and-seek.',7.0,5253,32.694,'2026-04-14 09:07:15','LBwfO9Hj6oQ','/oJD9KQFoObZmxAS1je56SIFVNJt.jpg'),(568332,'Taylor Swift: Reputation Stadium Tour','Taylor Swift: Reputation Stadium Tour',2018,125,'United States of America','en','Music','Taylor Swift, Charli xcx, Camila Cabello, David Cook, Amos Heller','Paul Dugdale','Taylor Swift takes the stage in Dallas for the Reputation Stadium Tour and celebrates a monumental night of music, memories and visual magic.',8.2,427,2.356,'2026-04-14 09:09:15','HIb_TlK2HAI','/u6oXUTtOuJRPdUgUuPAVVJPSKCo.jpg'),(569094,'Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse','Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse',2023,140,'United States of America','en','Animation, Action, Adventure, Science Fiction','Shameik Moore, Hailee Steinfeld, Brian Tyree Henry, Luna Lauren Vélez, Jake Johnson','Kemp Powers, Justin K. Thompson, Joaquim Dos Santos','After reuniting with Gwen Stacy, Brooklyn’s full-time, friendly neighborhood Spider-Man is catapulted across the Multiverse, where he encounters the Spider Society, a team of Spider-People charged with protecting the Multiverse\'s very existence. But when the heroes clash on how to handle a new threat, Miles finds himself pitted against the other Spiders and must set out on his own to save those he loves most.',8.3,8438,23.766,'2026-04-14 09:08:00','yFrxzaBLDQM','/8Vt6mWEReuy4Of61Lnj5Xj704m8.jpg'),(572154,'Rascal Does Not Dream of a Dreaming Girl','青春ブタ野郎はゆめみる少女の夢を見ない