 on behalf of her deeply smitten best friend – then she gets swept up in a love story of her own.',8.1,800,10.103,'2026-04-14 09:09:48','KFS4_qevE7M','/od22ftNnyag0TTxcnJhlsu3aLoU.jpg'),(858024,'Hamnet','Hamnet',2025,126,'United Kingdom','en','Drama, Romance, History','Jessie Buckley, Paul Mescal, Emily Watson, Joe Alwyn, Jacobi Jupe','Chloé Zhao','The powerful story of love and loss that inspired the creation of Shakespeare\'s timeless masterpiece, Hamlet.',7.7,1217,25.276,'2026-03-27 07:49:54','xYcgQMxQwmk','/vbeyOZm2bvBXcbgPD3v6o94epPX.jpg'),(872585,'Oppenheimer','Oppenheimer',2023,181,'United Kingdom','en','Drama, History','Cillian Murphy, Emily Blunt, Matt Damon, Robert Downey Jr., Florence Pugh','Christopher Nolan','The story of J. Robert Oppenheimer\'s role in the development of the atomic bomb during World War II.',8.0,11585,25.071,'2026-03-27 07:50:15','qiuSBWVdgLI','/8Gxv8gSFCU0XGDykEGv7zR1n2ua.jpg'),(875828,'Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man','Peaky Blinders: The Immortal Man',2026,112,'United Kingdom','en','Crime, Drama','Cillian Murphy, Barry Keoghan, Rebecca Ferguson, Tim Roth, Stephen Graham','Tom Harper','After his estranged son gets embroiled in a Nazi plot, self-exiled gangster Tommy Shelby must return to Birmingham to save his family — and his nation.',7.2,757,61.613,'2026-03-27 07:48:30','lcvUGs3xaDM','/gRMalasZEzsZi4w2VFuYusfSfqf.jpg'),(876792,'That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime the Movie: Scarlet Bond','劇場版 転生したらスライムだった件 紅蓮の絆編',2022,108,'Japan','ja','Animation, Fantasy, Adventure','Miho Okasaki, Makoto Furukawa, Megumi Toyoguchi, Tomoaki Maeno, Sayaka Senbongi','Yasuhito Kikuchi','A long-running conspiracy is swirling over a mysterious power wielded by the Queen in Raja, a small country west of Tempest. When a slime who evolved into a Demon Lord named Rimuru Tempest crosses paths with Hiiro, a survivor of the Ogre race, an incredible adventure packed with new characters begins. The power of bonds will be put to the test!',7.4,426,5.915,'202