ionship and exposing the fragile balance between love, identity, and motherhood.',6.2,472,9.245,'2026-04-14 09:10:57','2jzXHW6Qe70','/kajpShbFhOdpl6yCrLezMrr9tB4.jpg'),(1038392,'The Conjuring: Last Rites','The Conjuring: Last Rites',2025,136,'United States of America','en','Horror','Patrick Wilson, Vera Farmiga, Mia Tomlinson, Ben Hardy, Rebecca Calder','Michael Chaves','Paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren take on one last terrifying case involving mysterious entities they must confront.',6.9,1739,23.326,'2026-04-14 09:07:49','p4aWdkM5xF8','/byWgphT74ClOVa8EOGzYDkl8DVL.jpg'),(1043197,'Dust Bunny','Dust Bunny',2025,106,'United States of America','en','Fantasy, Action, Horror','Mads Mikkelsen, Sophie Sloan, Sigourney Weaver, David Dastmalchian, Sheila Atim','Bryan Fuller','Ten-year-old Aurora asks her hitman neighbor to kill the monster under her bed that she claims ate her family. To protect her, he must battle an onslaught of assassins while accepting that some monsters are real.',6.6,227,11.690,'2026-04-14 09:10:47','lQqmOjPDlWg','/qa5aZpO8tQqhlDaE0flalS1TuIS.jpg'),(1049471,'Outcome','Outcome',2026,84,'United States of America','en','Comedy, Drama','Keanu Reeves, Jonah Hill, Cameron Diaz, Matt Bomer, Susan Lucci','Jonah Hill','Reef Hawk, Hollywood\'s poster child since age six, is not okay. When he learns about an extortion plot tied to a mysterious video, Reef preemptively sets out on a redemption tour to make amends, confront his demons, and avoid getting canceled.',5.3,70,155.360,'2026-04-14 09:06:12','NQQqInahTAM','/kSzcpfbTy2pXHGvrVU2WhQTo6oU.jpg'),(1054867,'One Battle After Another','One Battle After Another',2025,162,'United States of America','en','Thriller, Crime, Comedy','Leonardo DiCaprio, Sean Penn, Chase Infiniti, Benicio del Toro, Regina Hall','Paul Thomas Anderson','Washed-up revolutionary Bob exists in a state of stoned paranoia, surviving off-grid with his spirited, self-reliant daughter, Willa. When his evil nemesis resurfaces after 16