uctions, and Swift\'s performance.',8.2,514,3.043,'2026-04-14 09:09:23','5UBl0rLEl0w','/jf3YO8hOqGHCupsREf5qymYq1n.jpg'),(1160360,'If I Had Legs I\'d Kick You','If I Had Legs I\'d Kick You',2025,113,'United States of America','en','Drama','Rose Byrne, Conan O\'Brien, A$AP Rocky, Danielle Macdonald, Delaney Quinn','Mary Bronstein','With her life crashing down around her, Linda attempts to navigate her child\'s mysterious illness, her absent husband, a missing person, and an increasingly hostile relationship with her therapist.',6.3,282,5.183,'2026-04-14 09:11:16','-oDLBRLkflo','/va0TQ9WprMXRqQAzY56vyqY0Yd5.jpg'),(1167307,'David','David',2025,109,'United States of America','en','Animation, Family, Drama','Brandon Engman, Brian Stivale, Shahar Taboch, Aaron Tavaler, Hector','Phil Cunningham, Brent Dawes','From the songs of his mother’s heart to the whispers of a faithful God, David’s story begins in quiet devotion. When the giant Goliath rises to terrorize a nation, a young shepherd armed with only a sling, a few stones, and unshakable faith steps forward. Pursued by power and driven by purpose, his journey tests the limits of loyalty, love, and courage—culminating in a battle not just for a crown, but for the soul of a kingdom.',8.1,126,35.139,'2026-03-27 07:49:15','gWgyI6_lR0A','/bESlrLOrsQ9gKzaGQGHXKOyIUtX.jpg'),(1168190,'The Wrecking Crew','The Wrecking Crew',2026,125,'United States of America','en','Action, Comedy, Crime, Mystery','Dave Bautista, Jason Momoa, Temuera Morrison, Morena Baccarin, Roimata Fox','Ángel Manuel Soto','Estranged half-brothers Jonny and James reunite after their father\'s mysterious death. As they search for the truth, buried secrets reveal a conspiracy threatening to tear their family apart.',6.9,886,61.605,'2026-03-27 07:48:46','v8R0xDczERo','/gbVwHl4YPSq6BcC92TQpe7qUTh6.jpg'),(1168719,'Silent Friend','Silent Friend',2026,147,'France','de','Drama','Tony Leung Chiu-wai, Léa Seydoux, Luna Wedler, Enzo Brumm, Sylvester Groth','Ildikó Enyedi'