Cv.jpg'),(1242501,'Icefall','Icefall',2025,99,'United States of America','en','Action, Crime, Thriller','Joel Kinnaman, Cara Jade Myers, Danny Huston, Graham Greene, Martin Sensmeier','Stefan Ruzowitzky','A young Indigenous game warden arrests an infamous poacher only to discover that the poacher knows the location of a plane carrying millions of dollars that has crashed in a frozen lake. When a group of criminals and dirty cops are alerted to the poacher’s whereabouts, the warden and the poacher team up to fight back and escape across the treacherous lake before the ice melts.',6.4,149,14.186,'2026-04-14 09:10:41','GimoXZs1BIs','/5Byv6nznAb2Izd0gHpODOXnuSbo.jpg'),(1242898,'Predator: Badlands','Predator: Badlands',2025,107,'United States of America','en','Action, Science Fiction, Adventure','Elle Fanning, Dimitrius Schuster-Koloamatangi, Ravi Narayan, Michael Homick, Stefan Grube','Dan Trachtenberg','Cast out from his clan, a young Predator finds an unlikely ally in a damaged android and embarks on a treacherous journey in search of the ultimate adversary.',7.7,2600,50.483,'2026-03-27 07:48:56','LkBqjfg8TGM','/erTRAi241eYF4K8KoGGOI8kFPox.jpg'),(1242937,'The Dreadful','The Dreadful',2026,94,'United States of America','en','Horror','Sophie Turner, Kit Harington, Marcia Gay Harden, Laurence O\'Fuarain, Jonathan Howard','Natasha Kermani','In medieval England, Anne and her domineering mother-in-law Morwen struggle to survive on the outskirts of society. But when a man from Anne\'s past returns from war, a curse begins to take shape through a mysterious knight and threatens to destroy them all.',6.2,60,7.195,'2026-04-14 09:11:06','KPBqxZPvYS0','/nhhJkYau8nQMFgauvOudDjwj9vA.jpg'),(1244531,'Beast of War','Beast of War',2025,87,'Australia','en','Thriller, Action, War, Horror','Mark Coles Smith, Joel Nankervis, Sam Delich, Maximillian Johnson, Lee Tiger Halley','Kiah Roache-Turner','When their boat sinks while crossing the Timor Sea during World War II, a troop of young Australian soldiers must find a way to survive the harsh seas on a quickly shrinking raft. Hundreds of miles from anywhere, they must confront interpersonal conflicts, enemy attacks, and the advances of one very large, very hungry great white shark.',6.2,113,4.334,'2026-04-14 09:11:26','l7uhBAKjJQY','/2xgDjVEOtu5LlbPEngxfbCqWEFg.jpg'),(1246049,'Dracula','Dracula',2025,130,'France','fr','Horror, Fantasy, Romance','Caleb Landry Jones, Zoë Bleu Sidel, Christoph Waltz, Matilda De Angelis, Ewens Abid','Luc Besson','In late 15th-century Eastern Europe, Prince Vlad II’s bride is brutally murdered. As a result, he renounces God and damns Heaven itself. Cursed with eternal life, Vlad is reborn as Dracula, an immortal warlord who defies fate in a blood-soaked crusade to wrench his lost love back from death.',7.1,1075,37.709,'2026-03-27 07:49:37','hverb7siYJ8','/dYRqA50yd0nB3qBR7AtWEJJQ8q.jpg'),(1254135,'13 Days, 13 Nights','13 jours, 13 nuits',2025,111,'France','fr','War, Action, Thriller','Roschdy Zem, Lyna Khoudri, Sidse Babett Knudsen, Christophe Montenez, Sina Parvaneh','Martin Bourboulon','Kabul, August 15, 2021. US troops are preparing to withdraw from Afghanistan, while the Taliban are marching on the capital to seize power. Amid the chaos, Commander Mohamed Bida and his men are in charge of security at the French embassy, the last Western mission to remain open. Trapped along with 500 people, left to their own devices, the team must reach the airport at all costs. A perilous mission with no guarantee of success to flee the hell of Kabul and rescue what remains of humanity.',6.7,206,4.133,'2026-04-14 09:11:33','K-8nIAQit3o','/orcdyqJZhbr731iN7yq7TK5zluc.jpg'),(1254808,'Nouvelle Vague','Nouvelle Vague',2025,106,'France','fr','Comedy, Drama, History','Guillaume Marbeck, Zoey Deutch, Aubry Dullin, Adrien Rouyard, Antoine Besson','Richard Linklater','After writing for Cahiers du cinéma, a young Jean-Luc Godard decides making films is the best film criticism. He convinces producer Georges de Beauregard to fund a low-budget feature, and creates a treatment with fellow New Wave filmmaker François Truffaut about a gangster couple. The result? Breathless, one of the first features of the Nouvelle Vague era of French cinema.',7.4,182,3.557,'2026-04-14 09:11:40','sRqWbsdACzg','/AfE7DZ0DPgme6I58dlYp1Bo9xeN.jpg'),(1262815,'The Choral','The Choral',2025,113,'United Kingdom','en','Comedy, Drama, Music','Ralph Fiennes, Roger Allam, Mark Addy, Alun Armstrong, Simon Russell Beale','Nicholas Hytner','As World War I rages on, Dr. Henry Guthrie takes over a British choral society that\'s lost most of its men to the army. The community soon discovers that the best response to the chaos of war is to make beautiful music together.',6.2,25,4.282,'2026-04-14 09:11:35','6zRVP-ZgMm8','/yQtms7CSM0CE0W6dYbLLAATb5rL.jpg'),(1263012,'Dead Man\'s Wire','Dead Man\'s Wire',2026,105,'United States of America','en','Crime, Drama, Thriller','Bill Skarsgård, Colman Domingo, Al Pacino, Dacre Montgomery, Myha\'la','Gus Van Sant','In 1977, former real estate developer Tony Kiritsis puts a dead man\'s switch on himself and the mortgage banker who did him wrong, demanding $5 million and a personal apology.',6.3,90,4.591,'2026-04-14 09:11:28','aHAwgnJL78Y','/dgSoeebklY0IGKWbp36r9FwRXlv.jpg'),(1265609,'War Machine','War Machine',2026,110,'Australia','en','Action, Science Fiction, Thriller','Alan Ritchson, Dennis Quaid, Stephan James, Jai Courtney, Esai Morales','Patrick Hughes','On one last grueling mission during Army Ranger training, a combat engineer must lead his unit in a fight against a giant otherworldly killing machine.',7.2,1423,147.992,'2026-03-27 07:48:34','AFuE1LRxm80','/tlPgDzwIE7VYYIIAGCTUOnN4wI1.jpg'),(1266127,'Ready or Not: Here I Come','Ready or Not: Here I Come',2026,108,'United States of America','en','Horror, Comedy','Samara Weaving, Kathryn Newton, Elijah Wood, Sarah Michelle Gellar, Shawn Hatosy','Matt Bettinelli-Olpin, Tyler Gillett','Moments after surviving