, Adventure','Emile Chérif, Lilli Falk, Johan von Ehrlich, Sophie Lelenta, Olivia Sinclair','Sven Unterwaldt Jr.','For shapeshifter Carag and his friends Brandon, Holly, and Lou, a new school year begins at Clearwater High. But first, the Woodwalker Council must decide whether Carag\'s mentor and patron of the school, Andrew Milling, is guilty of attacking humans. Carag is in a dilemma: he wants to put a stop to Milling\'s actions, but Milling promises to take him to his true puma family if he covers for him before the council.',6.3,6,3.200,'2026-04-14 09:11:39',NULL,'/9WrGxlyXnoV0ecLiA76wNaga8pK.jpg'),(1284460,'Alpha','Alpha',2025,128,'France','fr','Horror, Drama, Science Fiction, Thriller','Mélissa Boros, Tahar Rahim, Golshifteh Farahani, Emma Mackey, Finnegan Oldfield','Julia Ducournau','Alpha, a troubled 13-year-old lives with her single mom. Their world collapses the day she returns from school with a tattoo on her arm.',6.4,105,14.653,'2026-03-27 07:50:37','4Cc2A-YLARs','/PvdD2gTqSZfFWclP9ee4bqCn0B.jpg'),(1284496,'Cycle of Time','C\'était mieux demain',2025,103,'France','fr','Comedy, Science Fiction','Elsa Zylberstein, Didier Bourdon, Mathilde Le Borgne, Céline Fuhrer, Maxim Foster','Vinciane Millereau','In 1950s France, Helene and Michel lead a simple life until a freak accident in 2025 leads to Helene becoming a bank executive and Michel struggling with unemployment and depression. Their children grow up in a technology-dominated world.',6.2,72,22.121,'2026-04-14 09:08:16',NULL,'/63QJSYPjR3i3mwr4PmpvwfyLgDo.jpg'),(1287141,'Pillion','Pillion',2025,107,'United Kingdom','en','Romance, Drama, Comedy','Harry Melling, Alexander Skarsgård, Lesley Sharp, Douglas Hodge, Jake Shears','Harry Lighton','Colin, a timid gay man, is swept off his feet when Ray, an enigmatic and impossibly handsome biker, takes him on as his submissive in a crazy and erotic BDSM-focused relationship.',6.4,158,6.472,'2026-04-14 09:11:11','Gl8n5I-IIHU','/7Pd6ChSQjSXy4snJiorSdzg2cG3.jpg'),(1288