 strange family. But what unfolds is not what he could possibly expect.',7.3,69,12.382,'2026-03-27 07:50:37','qWkPjI-Brkc','/x0wD4Qxe0wulV0bxarsQ05PqDNF.jpg'),(1381216,'Lake Jesup: Bonecrusher\'s Revenge','Lake Jesup: Bonecrusher\'s Revenge',2024,87,'United States of America','en','Horror, Comedy, Adventure','Derek Russo, Jeff Benninghofen, Michael Houston King, Essex O\'Brien, Sarah Voigt','Michael Houston King','In 2003, Lake Jesup became the stage for a real-life horror story, as a monstrous alligator escaped from captivity and began a reign of terror. As the body count rose, a desperate hunt ensued to stop the creature.',6.3,42,45.834,'2026-03-27 07:48:39','CO4XWbTYYI0','/1Z1TgGXS1MD4DDfIkBNloM43vvj.jpg'),(1383731,'Protector','Protector',2026,90,'United States of America','en','Action, Thriller','Milla Jovovich, Matthew Modine, Isabel Myers, D. B. Sweeney, Don Harvey','Adrian Grünberg','Former war hero Nikki\'s peaceful life is shattered when her daughter is kidnapped. Thrust into the criminal underworld while hunted by cops and military, she must fight to rescue her child.',7.2,14,5.097,'2026-04-14 09:11:24','IRKGIuL3728','/hUv1DarjEMmQM38i9DvW9pHYPZ4.jpg'),(1387382,'Hunting Season','Hunting Season',2025,93,'United States of America','en','Action, Drama, Thriller','Mel Gibson, Shelley Hennig, Jordi Mollà, Sofia Hublitz, A.J. Buckley','Raja Collins','When a reclusive survivalist and his daughter rescue a mysterious, wounded woman from a river, they become entangled in a deadly web of violence and revenge, forcing them to confront a brutal criminal to survive.',6.9,181,41.198,'2026-03-27 07:49:12','O7vKuVadFmo','/cbryTyaWdqrKpQCw6K7zm2jrB5v.jpg'),(1401778,'Turbulence','Turbulence',2025,91,'United States of America','en','Thriller, Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy','Jeremy Irvine, Olga Kurylenko, Kelsey Grammer, Hera Hilmar, Lionel Robert Blanc','Claudio Fäh','Young married couple Zach and Emmy decide to take a hot air balloon trip across the Italian Dolomites to