tes of America','en','Horror, Thriller','Jim Cummings, Brittany Allen, Eric Nelsen, Corbin Bernsen, William Sadler','Gene Gallerano, William Pisciotta','When an oil tycoon and a famous adventurer vanish into the harsh winter of remote northern Alaska, a hand-picked rescue team endeavors to bring them home. What they don’t know is that they are trespassing on The Yeti’s territory, and the elements are the least of their worries.',6.9,21,90.778,'2026-04-14 09:06:28','7rXJdyv5cRQ','/qW22SucWPODisKufindxiI5Frxm.jpg'),(1419406,'The Shadow\'s Edge','The Shadow\'s Edge',2025,142,'China','zh','Action, Crime, Drama, Thriller','Jackie Chan, Zhang Zifeng, Tony Leung Ka-fai, Ci Sha, Jun','Larry Yang','Macau Police brings the tracking expert police officer out of retirement to help catch a dangerous group of professional thieves.',7.2,565,110.787,'2026-03-27 07:48:48','xvmADAJOoCg','/e0RU6KpdnrqFxDKlI3NOqN8nHL6.jpg'),(1424965,'Ice Skater','Ice Skater',2026,83,'Finland','en','Drama, Thriller','Thea Sofie Loch Næss, Nikos Koukas, Mimi Roivainen, Jasmin Simonen','Taavi Vartia','A survival drama about an ice skater stranded on an ice floe at the Arctic Sea. When the ice floe starts to float towards south and melt, the ice skater must use all means necessary to survive.',5.0,15,28.106,'2026-03-27 07:50:28','ShXeLbwaZLw','/m93BKabB7Je8WQACed58BXeHNNR.jpg'),(1426297,'Play Dead','Hazte la muerta',2025,72,'Argentina','es','Horror','Paula Brasca, Damián Del Castillo, Marta Quarleri, Milagros Ribet, Catalina Motto','Carlos Goitia','A woman wakes up injured in a basement surrounded by corpses. To survive, she pretends to be dead while a grotesque ritual unfolds in the house above.',5.9,39,26.481,'2026-03-27 07:48:48','Ry9pq-ggBS8','/ixWeYfvXT9AbfM0QPb9kwbVLbLV.jpg'),(1426964,'State of Fear','Salve Geral: Irmandade',2026,103,'Brazil','pt','Action, Thriller, Crime, Drama','Naruna Costa, Camilla Damião, Seu Jorge, David Santos, Marcélia Cartaxo','Pedro Morelli','As São Paulo erupts in an unprecedented wave of violence, a lawyer with underworld ties must strike a deal with the police to rescue her kidnapped niece.',5.6,63,24.805,'2026-03-27 07:49:27',NULL,'/3Eaqedg8MAlnP51GYY8MCSIdTnV.jpg'),(1429348,'The Stranger','L\'Étranger',2025,122,'France','fr','Drama, Crime','Benjamin Voisin, Rebecca Marder, Pierre Lottin, Denis Lavant, Swann Arlaud','François Ozon','Algiers, 1938. Meursault, a quiet and unassuming employee in his early thirties, attends his mother\'s funeral without shedding a tear. The next day, he begins a casual affair with Marie, a work colleague. He quickly slips back into his usual routine.',6.8,136,7.280,'2026-04-14 09:11:10','gR912kHSOlA','/nPv3Ay5ZzrCmmI3Mc5Q19Tut4ao.jpg'),(1430077,'Hokum','Hokum',2026,107,'United Arab Emirates','en','Horror, Mystery','Adam Scott, Peter Coonan, David Wilmot, Florence Ordesh, Will O\'Connell','Damian McCarthy','When novelist Ohm Bauman retreats to a remote inn to scatter his parents\' ashes, he is consumed by tales of a witch haunting the honeymoon suite. Disturbing visions and a shocking disappearance forces him to confront dark corners of his past.',0.0,0,4.230,'2026-04-14 09:11:32','jP2nDyQWBOU','/gC4FtEthYvx6XV2JHCQibf4P3FT.jpg'),(1432605,'My Father\'s Shadow','My Father\'s Shadow',2025,93,'Nigeria','en','Drama','Ṣọpẹ́ Dìrísù, Efon Wini, Godwin Egbo, Chibuike Marvellous Egbo, Tosin Adeyemi','Akinola Davies Jr.','Two young brothers explore Lagos with their estranged father during the 1993 Nigerian election crisis, witnessing both the city\'s magnitude and their father\'s daily struggles as political unrest threatens their journey home.',7.7,24,5.669,'2026-04-14 09:11:18','50ICTaEuQxg','/aF8AFFh3LJpF8An0KUM8SdTwfVt.jpg'),(1443374,'All the Good Eyes','森中有林',2026,117,'China','zh','Drama, Romance, Crime','Yu Hewei, Gao Yuanyuan, Han Geng, Zhang Tian\'ai, Qiao Shan','Zhi Zheng','The story chronicles four decades in the lives of a family deeply rooted in the soil of Northeast China. Through times of prosperity and hardship, they navigate cycles of love and hatred, fortune and misfortune. Though buffeted by the twists of fate, they never relinquish their steadfast guardianship of one another and the profound commitment to this ancestral land that sustains them.',0.0,0,4.824,'2026-04-14 09:11:25','SczqyZQRpAo','/lauBwkkT3dNqnLYAmd8YtRj7HD7.jpg'),(1443576,'Sundays','Los domingos',2025,112,'Spain','es','Drama','Blanca Soroa, Patricia López Arnaiz, Miguel Garcés, Juan Minujín, Mabel Rivera','Alauda Ruiz de Azúa','17-year-old Ainara is a student at a Catholic secondary school, and is about to take her final year exams and choose her future university course. To everyone’s surprise, this brilliant young girl announces to her family that she wants to take part in an induction period at a convent in order to embrace the religious life. Nobody was expecting this. While her father seems to be won over by his daughter’s aspirations, for Maite, Ainara’s aunt, this unexpected vocation is the manifestation of a deeper problem.',7.1,111,4.606,'2026-04-14 09:11:27','FRwwy6W2xh8','/3682SbY3rsNKsQzFpPUKrWdGmmx.jpg'),(1445363,'EPiC: Elvis Presley in Concert','EPiC: Elvis Presley in Concert',2026,98,'United States of America','en','Music, Documentary','Elvis Presley, James Burton, John Wilkinson, Charlie Hodge, Jerry Scheff','Baz Luhrmann','Long-lost footage from Elvis Presley\'s legendary Las Vegas residency in the 1970s woven together with rare 16mm footage from Elvis on Tour, and 8mm from the Graceland archive, plus recordings of Elvis telling \"his side of the story\" rediscovered during Baz Luhrmann\'s research for his 2022 film, Elvis.',8.0,42,7.512,'2026-04-14 09:11:03','2s_dCvUgOBI','/2K2NH5dforjT9kLcUC0eeBpdZkC.jpg'),(1448560,'Wildcat','Wildcat',2025,99,'United Kingdom','en','Action, Thriller','Kate Beckinsale, Lewis Tan, Alice Krige, Charles Dance, Rasmus Hardiker','James Nunn','An ex-black ops team reunite to pull off a desperate heist in order to save the life of their leader’s 