omance that could transform her life.',5.0,6,21.222,'2026-04-14 09:10:28','uYTMroh8pjI','/mJS0IF7Af3WpPRhSTDT6rGpiLzw.jpg'),(1456349,'It Was Just an Accident','Un simple accident',2025,103,'Iran','fr','Drama, Thriller, Crime, Mystery','Vahid Mobasseri, Mariam Afshari, Ebrahim Azizi, Hadis Pakbaten, Majid Panahi','Jafar Panahi','An unassuming mechanic is reminded of his time in an Iranian prison when he encounters a man he suspects to be his sadistic jailhouse captor.',7.1,514,6.369,'2026-04-14 09:11:10','9oHw2ubyWE4','/eNYGj2DG3n8OrVPTfYunpPW9uas.jpg'),(1462146,'S4: The Bob Lazar Story','S4: The Bob Lazar Story',2026,154,'Canada','en','Documentary','Bob Lazar, George Knapp, Gene Huff','Luigi Vendittelli','Over 35 years after Bob Lazar\'s revelations, this documentary exposes secrets of a facility the government still denies. Featuring Lazar\'s testimony, recreations, and new evidence, it reopens a case that continues to spark global curiosity',8.2,10,12.562,'2026-04-14 09:10:45','nqA_8tq3hlE','/cHWXWjUQg5mjuvQDimllZxusjD6.jpg'),(1465563,'A Poet','Un poeta',2025,123,'Colombia','es','Comedy, Drama','Ubeimar Rios, Rebeca Andrade, Guillermo Cardona, Alisson Correa, Margarita Soto','Simón Mesa Soto','An aging poet finds purpose mentoring Yurlady, a talented teen, though exposing her to the poetry scene might be unwise. His own poetic pursuits led nowhere, leaving him a stereotypical obscure writer.',7.4,25,17.773,'2026-04-14 09:10:32','xRyVkKYG3BA','/o0MRVa3XMUUIxiSCZYaJ1jGXdk.jpg'),(1470130,'The Mortuary Assistant','The Mortuary Assistant',2026,91,'United States of America','en','Horror, Mystery','Willa Holland, Paul Sparks, John Adams, Mark Steger, Shelly Gibson','Jeremiah Kipp','Rebecca Owens, a recent mortuary science graduate takes a night shift job at River Fields Mortuary. Initially, the job seems straightforward — embalming bodies, completing paperwork, and keeping things tidy. But once Rebecca starts working the night shift, things take a dark turn.',5.7,64,225.911,'2026-04-14 09:06:08','IU6q_BwYz2k','/72AoFPC5TY4DfJwXXS9rPwPeReD.jpg'),(1472951,'Infiltrate','Infiltrate',2026,93,'Canada','en','Action, Thriller','Orphée Ladouceur-Nguyen, Alain Moussi, Tim Rozon, Finn McCager Higgins, Lisa Berry','James Mark','In a city overrun by crime, government Agent Lily Chen is forced to choose between her duty and her family when her husband is kidnapped, and she’s blackmailed into assassinating high-level criminals to save him. As she delves deeper into the criminal underworld, Lily’s relentless pursuit of justice unravels a web of corruption, leading to a final, life-altering decision that will change her world forever.',6.1,6,54.315,'2026-04-14 09:06:43','dzVz0KqqwGE','/8Cw8GF9wG63kF8pRRXwOx2kXGt.jpg'),(1480382,'The Voice of Hind Rajab','صوت هند رجب',2025,89,'France','ar','Drama, History','Hind Rajab, Motaz Malhees, Saja Kilani, Amer Hlehel, Clara Khoury','Kaouther Ben Hania','January 29, 2024. Red Crescent volunteers receive an emergency call. A five-year old girl is trapped in a car under fire in Gaza, pleading for rescue. While trying to keep her on the line, they do everything they can to get an ambulance to her. Her name was Hind Rajab.',8.0,261,21.610,'2026-04-14 09:10:25','JkeKrG0YONQ','/q7M8kQB46T11vmDMD6E239jsqTz.jpg'),(1485085,'Homo Promo','Homo Promo',NULL,56,NULL,'en','Documentary','Bela Lugosi, Ingrid Thulin, Mae West, Edward D. Wood Jr.','Jenni Olson','This spectacular showcase of vintage movie trailers offers a crash course in lesbian, gay, bi and transgender (LGBT) movie history and a colorful look at nearly every major mainstream queer-themed film produced between 1953 and 1977! Archivist Jenni Olson is one of the world’s leading experts on LGBT film history — curated from her private collection of rare original 35mm coming attractions trailers, Homo Promo has entertained audiences at LGBT film festivals around the world offering a campy cavalcade of coming attractions. Please note: The condition of these original 35mm archival prints varies — enjoy the wear and tear and rest assured that they have now all been donated to the Outfest/UCLA Legacy Project for LGBT Film Preservation where they are now being properly cared for.',0.0,0,50.422,'2026-03-27 07:49:22',NULL,'/cpbL1zypKLoWDUBdfhAoEuQ9Uff.jpg'),(1487320,'The Giant Falls','El último gigante',2026,100,'Argentina','es','Drama','Oscar Martínez, Matías Mayer, Inés Estévez, Luis Luque, Silvia Kutika','Marcos Carnevale','Follows Boris, a charismatic tour guide who unexpectedly reunites with his estranged father Julián. Their tense and emotional encounters explore past wounds and the possibility of forgiveness.',6.8,16,18.207,'2026-04-14 09:10:27','E2LpTcCIZD8','/lARMzlnHtusEnY8LrTmNID92CJo.jpg'),(1488684,'The Robbers','The Robbers',2009,39,'United Kingdom','en','Comedy','Hugh Dennis, Claire Skinner, Tyger Drew-Honey, Daniel Roche, Ramona Marquez','Andy Hamilton, Guy Jenkin','It\'s Boxing Day and already Karen is making New Year resolutions - chiefly for others - and the family have been burgled,though selectively,causing Sue to cheat on the insurance claim. Sue and Jake go to collect Grandad from the retirement home where he now lives,only to find he has sloped off to the pub again with Scots mate Mac. Sue ends up asking Mac back for dinner though his thick accent creates a language barrier for Karen. Sue\'s divorced friend Jane is also invited and though the children fail to appreciate her present for them,a goat donated to Oxfam,Pete feels sorry for her and is glad that the Brockmans have given a Christmas to lonely strangers - until a W.P.C. turns up with another old boy who has gone walkabout.',0.0,0,28.808,'2026-03-27 07:49:55',NULL,'/tZkY4zEdMykflnEuPWzJ7lE7d19.jpg'),(1493859,'Pizza Movie','Pizza Movie',2026,98,'United States of America','en','Comedy','Gaten Matarazzo, Sean Giambrone, Lulu Wilson, Jack Martin, Peyton Elizabeth Lee','Nick Kocher, Brian McElhaney','A group of college students go downstairs to their dorm lobby to get a delivery pizza. There\'s only one issue: They\'re insanely high on a homemade drug, turning their simple journey down two sets of stairs into a mind-bendingly transformative quest.',6.5,66,43.739,'2026-04-14 09:06:51','fOzF87PFGnw','/v2qH9CiGWup1Ddzai76ofgtSTAh.jpg'),(1497970,'Tom and Jerry: Forbidden Compass','猫和老鼠：星盘奇缘',2025,104,'China','zh','Animation, Comedy, Family, Fantasy, Adventure','Jiang Wen, Shun Zi, Lan Long, Tu Xiongfei, Li Baixin','Zhang Gang','During a chase inside a museum, Tom and Jerry find a magical object and end up being transported through time. Lost in a distant era, they will need to work together to find a way back home.',6.2,32,21.125,'2026-04-14 09:08:20','lScTuXgrf4k','/5qttWFjsO62k88civZaDMHiBTvy.jpg'),(1507199,'Careless','Careless',2025,88,'Australia','en','Documentary','Margaret Thomson, Olivia Cornwell, Jane Cornwell, Sarah Holland-Batt, Beverly','Sue Thomson','When director Sue Thomson’s 89-year-old mum, Margaret, begins to need additional help with day-to-day life, they face a decision that most families will encounter: whether to consider a residential aged-care facility; and, if so, how to find a suitable one amid a sector with a reputation for neglect and mistreatment. Margaret’s story becomes a springboard for an investigation of the political history of aged care in Australia, marred by a 40-year bipartisan privatisation agenda. As we hear from advocates, journalists and senior citizens who have experienced the system, a group of schoolkids discuss the situation we’ve reached with aged care and where we need to go from here – and of what they, and we, can expect in the future.',0.0,0,21.759,'2026-04-14 09:07:54',NULL,'/dXfkTfzN1CaNbhGULhl4vGYSVOY.jpg'),(1510378,'The Sexpert','The Sexpert',1972,61,'United States of America','en','Comedy','Stan Ross, Jaime Lyn Bauer, Marvin Miller, Steve Vinovich','Alan Roberts','Hopelessly inept clod Finster Fahrquart desperately tries to get into the swing of the 70\'s sexual revolution and figure out a way to succeed with the ladies. Following a series of disastrous encounters with such folks as an aggressive farmer\'s daughter, a not so innocent virgin, and an unhappy housewife, Finster decides to attend an orgy.',0.0,0,36.605,'2026-03-27 07:49:46',NULL,NULL),(1510583,'Rakkhosh','রাক্ষস',2026,141,'Bangladesh','bn','Action, Romance','Siam Ahmed, Susmita Chatterjee, Shataf Figar, Ali Raj, Samm Bhattacharyya','Mehedi Hasan Hridoy','The story about a man pushed to his limits by love and greed, who eventually embraces his darker side to seek justice or revenge in a world filled with \"monsters.\"',5.5,1,5.745,'2026-04-14 09:11:17','CD-kNjIw85E','/a2fCCiq14zbk7VGyUAgZvqIMxr6.jpg'),(1511417,'Bāhubali: The Epic','Bāhubali: The Epic',2025,224,'India','te','Action, Drama','Prabhas, Rana Daggubati, Anushka Shetty, Ramya Krishnan, Sathyaraj','S. S. Rajamouli','When a mysterious child is found by a tribal couple near a roaring waterfall, they raise him as their own. As he grows, Sivudu is drawn to the world beyond the cliffs, where he discovers the ancient kingdom of Mahishmati, ruled by a cruel tyrant, haunted by rebellion, and bound to his past. What begins as a quest for love soon unravels a legacy of betrayal, sacrifice, and a forgotten prince.',6.0,35,27.242,'2026-03-27 07:49:45','q8nbZbHRcEg','/z9YIo2qscyaXYgRqIdRJtND3bw8.jpg'),(1519168,'The Jester 2','The Jester 2',2025,87,'United States of America','en','Horror, Thriller, Crime','Michael Sheffield, Kaitlyn Trentham, Dingani Beza, Hassen Kacem, Jessica Ambuehl','Colin Krawchuk','When teen magician Max crosses paths with the sinister Jester on Halloween night, she must outsmart a supernatural killer whose magic is all too real and whose tricks always end up in blood.',6.2,61,4.889,'2026-04-14 09:11:22','7ogVp-d-CdE','/47dsw1jSOV0Be5zmy7CtLhYpqU.jpg'),(1523145,'Your Heart Will Be Broken','Твое сердце будет разбито',2026,200,'Russia','ru','Romance, Drama','Veronika Zhuravleva, Daniel Vegas, Alya Mayer, Maksim Saprykin, Evgeniya Loza','Mikhail Vaynberg','High school student Polina is saved from bullying at her new school and makes a deal with the main bully Bars: he must pretend to be her boyfriend and protect her, and she must do everything he says. During this game, the couple develops real feelings, but her family and classmates have reasons to separate the lovers.',7.1,58,732.326,'2026-03-27 07:48:33',NULL,'/7wIBfBl2gejt6xHxNSK0reVIm7E.jpg'),(1526650,'Mudborn','泥娃娃',2025,111,'Taiwan','zh','Horror, Thriller','Tony Yang, Cecilia Choi, Derek Chang, Tracy Chou, Puff Kuo','Shieh Meng-ju','Hsu-Chuan, who works at a game company, accidentally brings home a broken clay doll from a haunted house while developing a new horror VR game. Unexpectedly, his pregnant wife, Mu-Hua, a cultural relic restorer, develops an obsession with the doll and relentlessly tries to repair it. As strange things begin to happen in the house, Mu-Hua\'s condition deteriorates, and Hsu-Chuan, at his wits\' end, seeks help from a spiritual medium, Ah-Sheng. Meanwhile, the horrifying secret hidden behind the clay doll begins to surface.',6.6,17,118.546,'2026-04-14 09:06:18','I--CxbFKzPA','/ifYNeKwpyKUTtjkUExrqTc65L2p.jpg'),(1539104,'JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution','劇場版 呪術廻戦「渋谷事変 特別編集版」×「死滅回游 先行上映」',2025,88,'Japan','ja','Animation, Action, Fantasy','Junya Enoki, Megumi Ogata, Koji Yusa, Daisuke Namikawa, Yuma Uchida','Shota Goshozono','A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away. Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident. In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji\'s execution for his perceived crimes. A compilation movie of Shibuya Incident including the first two episodes of the Culling Games arc.',5.9,92,48.880,'2026-03-27 07:49:24','XeoQg5PVOLI','/v0s3dx6am0RzfsuK3KdEy8ZoCDs.jpg'),(1542995,'Bonolota Express','বনলতা এক্সপ্রেস',2026,153,'Bangladesh','bn','Drama, Comedy','Mosharraf Karim, Chanchal Chowdhury, Sabila Nur, Sariful Razz, Zakia Bari Mamo','Tanim Noor','On a foggy winter journey, the Bonolota Express carries strangers burdened by secrets whose lives begin to collide within the train’s confined corridors. As the night unfolds, personal and political crises erupt, exposing hidden grief, moral decay, and moments of unexpected compassion amid chaos and revolt. By dawn, the train moves on, leaving its passengers irrevocably changed by a single journey where illusions collapse and human truths emerge.',0.0,0,21.848,'2026-04-14 09:08:20','ZTZUaHsfR8o','/kHVPmcGyCUNIKmHZ2tlosvyEjMP.jpg'),(1555895,'The Aryan Papers','The Aryan Papers',2026,86,'United Kingdom','en','Adventure, War, History','Cara Chase, Leona Clarke, Richard Hawley, Alex Reece, Matthew Hendrickson','Danny Patrick','Stuttgart, 1942: Nazis have cleared Jewish communities from towns and Villages. Two German-born Jewish children flee Nazis who have killed their family, escorted by Gisella, part of the Lebensborn, an SS Master Race program.',4.0,1,120.120,'2026-03-28 06:44:53','y9zXCJTutWI','/30fQ2nYMyv5TjyEm3j9JwgTa3ZW.jpg'),(1561758,'It Takes a Village','Podlasie',2026,94,'Poland','pl','Romance, Comedy','Anna Seniuk, Artur Barciś, Filip Gurłacz, Joanna Trzepiecińska, Anna Szymańczyk','Łukasz Kośmicki','When financial trouble forces Halina to call off her wedding, her friends and family decide to hatch a wild plan to bring in tourist money.',4.7,9,11.202,'2026-04-14 09:10:42','DrhAhSCqJws','/znUVVJh0WSCHAhiJ6Att5qhmAzG.jpg'),(1572073,'The Deadly Little Mermaid','The Deadly Little Mermaid',202