rce.',6.2,65,23.538,'2026-03-27 07:49:31','uXRFha7MLTM','/fYqSOkix4rbDiZW0ACNnvZCpT6X.jpg'),(1601243,'Oscar Shaw','Oscar Shaw',2026,93,NULL,'en','Action, Crime, Thriller, Western','Michael Jai White, Tyrese Gibson, Isaiah Washington, Andrew C. English Jr., Cecile Cubiló','R. Ellis Frazier, Justin Nesbitt','After retiring from the police force, a relentless detective haunted by the tragic loss of his closest friend sets out on a perilous quest for vengeance, seeking redemption and fighting to restore justice to the streets he once swore to protect.',6.5,29,25.964,'2026-03-27 07:49:44','ZMlCJQ2SefU','/tsE3nySukwrfUjouz8vzvKTcXNC.jpg'),(1610418,'The House on Haunted Grounds','The House on Haunted Grounds',2026,69,NULL,'en','Horror','Logan Wallace, Andrew Thomas, Stuart Maxheimer, Cashmere Moniqué, Dylan DeVane','Brendan Rudnicki','They walked into a haunted house with a history of possession and murder. The victims never came out, but the footage did.',4.7,5,86.681,'2026-04-14 09:06:22','uXHjb8_z9bE','/750RNSHr25GQcCr2Ws8iSGrHJA9.jpg'),(1611398,'Un hombre por semana','Un hombre por semana',2026,97,'Mexico','es','Comedy, Romance, Drama','Ana de la Reguera, Roberto Quijano, Carlos \'Capi\' Pérez, Fernando Álvarez Rebeil, Patricia Garza','Marco Polo Constandse, Ana de la Reguera','A divorced woman reconstructs her life and opens herself to love. Her search for dating apps takes her through fun and unpredictable moments to discover self-love.',6.4,18,31.772,'2026-03-27 07:50:04',NULL,'/rHwOvosfDFRsjBihdh9dIHnMgbO.jpg'),(1620551,'Feel My Voice','Non abbiam bisogno di parole',2026,105,'Italy','it','Music, Drama, Comedy','Sarah Toscano, Serena Rossi, Carola Insolera, Emilio Insolera, Antonio Iorillo','Luca Ribuoli','A teenager, the only hearing member of a deaf family, finds her voice and learns to believe in herself through her passion for singing.',6.6,65,27.129,'2026-04-14 09:07:26','jcDax7jiSqM','/4Tf0qTA73XLhBnfP6YgvqtLZBnt.jpg'),(1630433,'The Red Line','เส้นตาย สายลวง',