e studio audience and hosted by Alex Cooper of \'Call Her Daddy\' fame, Miley Cyrus reflects on the creation and impact of the series, with never-before-seen archival footage, and some of the show\'s most memorable sets will be \'brought back to life\' — including the Stewart family living room and the legendary Hannah Montana closet.',7.2,68,12.420,'2026-03-27 07:50:05','QBjEeCFdc2o','/2BZ0bij5ORSvfDepCDD8CqVcpaG.jpg'),(1641319,'Sniper: No Nation','Sniper: No Nation',2026,96,'United States of America','en','Action, Thriller','Chad Michael Collins, Ryan Robbins, Manuel Rodriguez-Saenz, Josh Brener, Tom Berenger','Trevor Calverley','Brandon Beckett and Agent Zero lead a rescue mission in Venezuela when their friends are taken hostage.',6.0,24,260.730,'2026-04-14 09:06:06','-smVu1cxPm8','/3T9nAX0jAp0iT18ex25BlZEpRDb.jpg'),(1646142,'Terrestrial','Terrestrial',2024,NULL,NULL,'en','Horror','Dane-randall bacon, Deena Bacon, Randall J. Bacon, Rayden Bacon, Derek Bega','Alex Farnham',NULL,10.0,1,46.991,'2026-03-27 07:49:44',NULL,'/g4PBZlyVm2cWgL4jAy7WKEblB4t.jpg'),(1646787,'Sundutan','Sundutan',2026,70,'Philippines','tl','Drama','Allison Ross, Jade Esguerra, Mark Dionisio, Zia Zamora, Primo Angeles','Rodante Pajemna Jr.','A hole on the wall accidentally connects two women emotionally and physically. Forbidden love, greed, betrayal... what lies beyond the hole? And for how long can they keep covering it up?',4.0,1,61.390,'2026-03-27 07:49:29','iVOyYHzvbKc','/2neZgVuY7prWIak5hhNKT53Hk0N.jpg'),(1650558,'Abot Langit','Abot Langit',2026,70,'Philippines','tl','Romance','Aliya Raymundo, JC Tan, Jio Yoshida, Zel Fernandez, Jetleline Esquivel','Topel Lee','The relationship of a couple is tested when the girl’s first official flight pairs her with a confident senior pilot, jealousy and power dynamics surface in the training ground. The girl is now torn between her present relationship and new temptation she can’t resist.',5.0,1,30.090,'2026-03-27 07:49:33','MMvU2xSos4s','/5lVYe4aSimW