g interviews from members of the casting, production design, costume design, and creature effects teams, follow the behind-the-scenes journey of bringing the Harry Potter books to the small screen. Find out how the new Golden Trio were found, and celebrate the commitment to detail of the artists, craftspeople, and technicians who have come together to bring the wizarding world to life.',7.9,24,15.491,'2026-04-14 09:10:31','0TsRwfhgeYc','/aq8jKIfASiOR6wz9FCeeCH90xZq.jpg');
